Active Sig:                 (-0.5)
Passive Sig (emit.refl):    (-1/-2) 
			    (-1.5/-2 at 50 MW power)
			    (-2.5/-2 when shut down)

Or (the short form): Signature (act/emit/ref): -1/-1/-2




